Originally ripped by Terminal Escape, posted on August 15, 2023 Description from Terminal Escape:
 I want to say that it's the guitars that make this tape....but really it's the whole damn thing. You'll hear hints of fellow Twin Cities rockers URANIUM CLUB mingling with wild off kilter punk and then boom there's shades of chaotic '90s indie/emo and why oh why does it all work so damn well together? I can't answer that, young punks...but I'm here to share, not question. Kinda like therapy. VOL. 1
